{"tid":977201,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人開教室　教日本人　正宗香港料理","createTime":"2019-01-11T04:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T08:59:45.000Z","uid":47714,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0de95c26250e8c3414020079dad63cd4ba5d210","tid":977201,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lusdeli.wixsite.com/lusdeli/cooking-class\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flusdeli.wixsite.com%2Flusdeli%2Fcooking-class&d=48mk7pwonB40V2PL3zWGtgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=aa3f1979\" target=\"_blank\">https://lusdeli.wixsite.com/lusdeli/cooking-class</a><br />\n<br />\n中華風ではなく、<br />\n日本にある中国風料理ではなく、<br />\n中国国内の中国料理ではなく、<br />\n徹底的に香港そのものの味の​再現にこだわっています<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劣譯：<br />\n不是中華風<br />\n不是日本的中國風料理<br />\n不是中國國內的中國料理<br />\n是徹底的香港真正味道重現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lusdeli.wixsite.com/lusdeli/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flusdeli.wixsite.com%2Flusdeli%2Fabout-us&d=48mk7pwonB40V2PL3zWGtgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f83b40e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lusdeli.wixsite.com/lusdeli/about-us</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/cd797e_fb34c338561e41c79bdab1c028b474a9~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_233,h_155,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/161130_033_edited.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fcd797e_fb34c338561e41c79bdab1c028b474a9~mv2.jpg%2Fv1%2Ffill%2Fw_233%2Ch_155%2Cal_c%2Cq_80%2Cusm_0.66_1.00_0.01%2F161130_033_edited.jpg&h=58ada894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nProfile<br />\n<br />\n櫻井　景子　sakuraikeikoｈ<br />\n<br />\n香港料理食文化研究家<br />\n<br />\n日本香港協会会員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lusdeli.wixsite.com/lusdeli/cooking-class-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flusdeli.wixsite.com%2Flusdeli%2Fcooking-class-hong-kong&d=48mk7pwonB40V2PL3zWGtgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=24d7fb7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://lusdeli.wixsite.com/lusdeli/cooking-class-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n香港點心と香港スイーツ<br />\nHong Kong Dim Sum＆Sweets　Hands-ON Lesson<br />\n<br />\nBeginners Class 初級クラス<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCode:001　<br />\n<br />\n茶葉蛋　お茶たまご<br />\n<br />\n雑果蝦沙律蓋　海老のフルーツカップ<br />\n<br />\n馬拉糕　マレー風蒸しカップカステラ<br />\n​​​<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCode:002　<br />\n<br />\n沙律明蝦芝士春巻　えびチーズ春巻<br />\n<br />\n港式奶茶　香港式ミルクティ<br />\n<br />\n法蘭西多士　香港式フレンチトースト <br />\n<br />\n自製咖椰醬　手作りカヤジャム<br />\n<br />\n自製花生醤​　手作りピーナッツバター<br />\n​​​<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCode:003　<br />\n<br />\n蝦多士　シュリンプトースト<br />\n<br />\n椰汁雑果西米露　ココナツミルクタピオカスープ<br />\n<br />\n​​　　　　　  　<br />\n<br />\nCode:004  <br />\n<br />\n咖喱鶏粒角　カレーチキンパイ<br />\n<br />\n木瓜雪耳糖水　パパイヤ白きくらげスープ<br />\n<br />\n​​<br />\n<br />\nCode:005 　<br />\n<br />\n山竹牛肉球 <br />\n<br />\n煎薄罉<br />\n<br />\n南瓜粟米露<br />\n<br />\n​​​<br />\n<br />\nCode:006　<br />\n<br />\n香煎蓮藕餅　れんこん餅<br />\n<br />\n椰汁桂花糕　金木犀とココナツミルクのゼリー<br />\n<br />\n​​​<br />\n<br />\nCode:007    <br />\n<br />\n珍珠丸子　もち米しゅうまい<br />\n<br />\n黒糯米椰汁露　黒もち米ココナツしるこ<br />\n<br />\n​​​<br />\n<br />\nCode:008  　<br />\n<br />\n上湯鮮蝦腐皮卷　海老湯葉ロールのスープ仕立て<br />\n<br />\n鮮蝦腐皮巻　えびのゆば春巻き　　　　　　　　<br />\n<br />\n蠔油鮮竹巻　　 　揚げゆばあんかけ<br />\n<br />\n白果腐竹意米糖水　ぎんなんはとむぎゆばしるこ<br />\n<br />\n​<br />\n<br />\nCode:009  　<br />\n<br />\n春巻 　香港式春巻き　<br />\n<br />\n芋頭西米露　タロイモのタピオカしるこ<br />\n<br />\n​​<br />\n<br />\nCode:010  　<br />\n<br />\n豉汁肉排　豚肉トウチー蒸し<br />\n<br />\n笑口棗　スマイルドーナッツ<br />\n<br />\n薑汁番薯湯　サツマイモのしょうがシロップ"},{"pid":"f21dc86f9996cafa691b916747336fb63eb820fd","tid":977201,"uid":56698,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:31:32.000Z","msg":"香港人都唔識整啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5e2916ca915f3a6bfbcf2295dd39c684611cef","tid":977201,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"有Annie師傅喎  好撚過做tvb啲西工多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061b50b37debfce1bcddd3edb0fe2d7e4616ae64","tid":977201,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"好似好熟口面"},{"pid":"a8bb3c754ee11ac9d5a4ce75f1e63f3fca3abe3b","tid":977201,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"牛肉加蔥花 要烏冬嗎"},{"pid":"bba42a04a4bd0e473244051e1a0a2848dc259d1a","tid":977201,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"點可以無的士飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55133ea665c17c43555b9a68c6117a43510c388","tid":977201,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"真係好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牛肉球呢啲都走去整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}